cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with transfer learning for medical imaging, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models and their corresponding pretrained weights, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of performance on medical imaging tasks involves the use of metrics and statistical analysis, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
